Customer accounting code (s.code_compta): Code or empty to be auto-created
Vendor accounting code (s.code_compta_fo: Code or empty to be auto-created
Country code (s.fk_pays): US/FR/DE etc. matches field "code" in table "vg_c_country"
Employees (s.fk_effectif): 1/2/3/5: represents one of the five ranges of employees
Third-party type (s.fk_typent): matches field "id" (1-9 etc.) OR "code" (TE_SMALL etc.) in table "vg_c_typent"
Default language (s.default_lang): en_US / es_ES etc...matches a language directory in htdocs/langs/
Canvas (s.canvas): empty / a custom canvas form layout url e.g. mycanvas@mymodule
Currency (s.multicurrency_code): GBP/USD etc... matches field "code_iso" in table "vg_c_currencies"
